Author: Timwi
Description: Solve a 4×4 Sudoku in which every cell is encoded in a different way (Letters, Digits, Arrows, Binary, Braille, Tap Code, Morse Code, Semaphores, Maritime Flags, Mahjong tiles, Card suits, Snooker balls, Astrology elements, chess pieces, Simon Samples sounds, and The Cube symbols). Tags: 4x4-grid, 4×4-grid, 2-panels
Name: Kudosudoku
